# Reference: https://clang.llvm.org/docs/ClangFormatStyleOptions.html
---
BasedOnStyle: LLVM
IndentWidth: 4
---
Language: Cpp
ColumnLimit: 120
BreakBeforeBraces: Custom
BraceWrapping:
  AfterEnum: false
  AfterStruct: false
  SplitEmptyFunction: false
  AfterClass: true
  AfterFunction: true
  AfterControlStatement: Always
...